{"book": 24, "chapter": 51, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "再審判巴比倫"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必使毀滅的風颳起，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "攻擊巴比倫和住在立加米的人。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我要打發外邦人來到巴比倫，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "簸揚她，使她的地空虛。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在她遭禍的日子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們要周圍攻擊她。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "拉弓的，要向拉弓的和貫甲挺身的射箭。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不要憐惜她的少年人；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要滅盡她的全軍。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們必在迦勒底人之地被殺仆倒，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在巴比倫的街上被刺透。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 以色列和猶大雖然境內充滿違背以色列聖者的罪，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "卻沒有被他的神－萬軍之耶和華丟棄。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們要從巴比倫中逃奔，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "各救自己的性命！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不要陷在她的罪孽中一同滅亡；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為這是耶和華報仇的時候，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他必向巴比倫施行報應。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫素來是耶和華手中的金杯，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使天下沉醉；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "萬國喝了她的酒就顛狂了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫忽然傾覆毀壞；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要為她哀號；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "為止她的疼痛，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "拿乳香或者可以治好。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我們想醫治巴比倫，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她卻沒有治好。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "離開她吧！我們各人歸回本國；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為她受的審判通於上天，達到穹蒼。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華已經彰顯我們的公義。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "來吧！我們可以在錫安"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "報告耶和華－我們神的作為。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們要磨尖了箭頭，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "抓住盾牌。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph-no-indent", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "耶和華定意攻擊巴比倫，將她毀滅，所以激動了米底亞君王的心；因這是耶和華報仇，就是為自己的殿報仇。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們要豎立大旗，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "攻擊巴比倫的城牆；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要堅固瞭望臺，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "派定守望的設下埋伏；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為耶和華指着巴比倫居民所說的話、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "所定的意，他已經作成。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "住在眾水之上多有財寶的啊，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你的結局到了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你貪婪之量滿了！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "萬軍之耶和華指着自己起誓說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必使敵人充滿你，像螞蚱一樣；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們必吶喊攻擊你。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "頌讚神的詩歌"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華用能力創造大地，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用智慧建立世界，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用聰明鋪張穹蒼。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他一發聲，空中便有多水激動；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他使雲霧從地極上騰。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他造電隨雨而閃，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "從他府庫中帶出風來。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "各人都成了畜類，毫無知識。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "各銀匠都因他的偶像羞愧；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他所鑄的偶像本是虛假的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "其中並無氣息，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "都是虛無的，是迷惑人的工作，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "到追討的時候，必被除滅。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 雅各的分不像這些，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因他是造作萬有的主；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 以色列也是他產業的支派。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "萬軍之耶和華是他的名。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華的鐵鎚"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你是我爭戰的斧子和打仗的兵器；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要用你打碎列國，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用你毀滅列邦；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "用你打碎馬和騎馬的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用你打碎戰車和坐在其上的；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "用你打碎男人和女人；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用你打碎老年人和少年人；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用你打碎壯丁和處女；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "用你打碎牧人和他的羣畜；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用你打碎農夫和他一對牛；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用你打碎省長和副省長。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "懲罰巴比倫"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說：「我必在你們眼前報復巴比倫人和迦勒底居民在錫安所行的諸惡。」"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你這行毀滅的山哪，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "就是毀滅天下的山，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我與你反對。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必向你伸手，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "將你從山巖滾下去，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使你成為燒毀的山。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "人必不從你那裏取石頭為房角石，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也不取石頭為根基石；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你必永遠荒涼。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "要在境內豎立大旗，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在各國中吹角，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使列國預備攻擊巴比倫，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "將亞拉臘、米尼、亞實基拿各國招來攻擊她；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又派軍長來攻擊她，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使馬匹上來如螞蚱，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "使列國和米底亞君王，與省長和副省長，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並他們所管全地之人，都預備攻擊她。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "地必震動而瘠苦；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因耶和華向巴比倫所定的旨意成立了，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使巴比倫之地荒涼，無人居住。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫的勇士止息爭戰，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "藏在堅壘之中。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的勇力衰盡，好像婦女一樣。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫的住處有火着起，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "門閂都折斷了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "跑報的要彼此相遇，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "送信的要互相迎接，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "報告巴比倫王說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "城的四方被攻取了，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "渡口被佔據了，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "葦塘被火燒了，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "兵丁也驚慌了。"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "萬軍之耶和華－以色列的神如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫城好像踹穀的禾場；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "再過片時，收割她的時候就到了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 以色列人說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫王尼布甲尼撒吞滅我，壓碎我，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使我成為空虛的器皿。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他像大魚將我吞下，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "用我的美物充滿他的肚腹，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "又將我趕出去。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 34, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 錫安的居民要說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫以強暴待我，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "損害我的身體，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願這罪歸給她。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 耶路撒冷人要說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "願流我們血的罪歸到迦勒底的居民。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶和華要幫助以色列"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 35, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 36, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "所以，耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 36, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必為你伸冤，為你報仇；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 36, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必使巴比倫的海枯竭，使她的泉源乾涸。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 36, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 37, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫必成為亂堆，為野狗的住處，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 37, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "令人驚駭、嗤笑，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 37, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "並且無人居住。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 37, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 38, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們要像少壯獅子咆哮，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 38, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "像小獅子吼叫。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 38, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 39, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們火熱的時候，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 39, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必為他們設擺酒席，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 39, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們沉醉，好叫他們快樂，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 39, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "睡了長覺，永不醒起。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 39, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 39, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 40, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必使他們像羊羔、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 40, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "像公綿羊和公山羊下到宰殺之地。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "巴比倫的命運"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 40, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 41, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 示沙克 何竟被攻取？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 41, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "天下所稱讚的何竟被佔據？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 41, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫在列國中何竟變為荒場？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 41, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 42, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "海水漲起，漫過巴比倫；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 42, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她被許多海浪遮蓋。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 42, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 43, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "她的城邑變為荒場、旱地、沙漠，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 43, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "無人居住，無人經過之地。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 43, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 44, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我必刑罰巴比倫的彼勒，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 44, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他吐出所吞的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 44, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "萬民必不再流歸他那裏；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 44, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫的城牆也必坍塌了。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 44, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 45, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我的民哪，你們要從其中出去！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 45, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "各人拯救自己，躲避耶和華的烈怒。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 45, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 46, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們不要心驚膽怯，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 46, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "也不要因境內所聽見的風聲懼怕；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 46, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為這年有風聲傳來；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 46, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那年也有風聲傳來，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 46, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "境內有強暴的事，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 46, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "官長攻擊官長。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 46, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 47, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "日子將到，我必刑罰巴比倫雕刻的偶像。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 47, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她全地必然抱愧；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 47, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她被殺的人必在其中仆倒。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 47, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 48, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那時，天地和其中所有的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 48, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必因巴比倫歡呼，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 48, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為行毀滅的要從北方來到她那裏。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 48, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 48, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 49, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫怎樣使以色列被殺的人仆倒，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 49, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "照樣她全地被殺的人也必在巴比倫仆倒。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "給在巴比倫的以色列人的信息"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 49, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 50, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你們躲避刀劍的要快走，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 50, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "不要站住！"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 50, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要在遠方記念耶和華，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 50, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "心中追想耶路撒冷。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 50, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 51, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我們聽見辱罵就蒙羞，滿面慚愧，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 51, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為外邦人進入耶和華殿的聖所。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 51, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 52, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 52, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "日子將到，我必刑罰巴比倫雕刻的偶像，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 52, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "通國受傷的人必唉哼。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 52, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 53, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 巴比倫雖升到天上，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 53, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "雖使她堅固的高處更堅固，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 53, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "還有行毀滅的從我這裏到她那裏。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 53, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是耶和華說的。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "巴比倫滅亡"}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 53, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 54, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "有哀號的聲音從巴比倫出來；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 54, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "有大毀滅的響聲從迦勒底人之地發出。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 54, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 55, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "因耶和華使巴比倫變為荒場，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 55, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使其中的大聲滅絕。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 55, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "仇敵彷彿眾水，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 55, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "波浪匉訇，響聲已經發出。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 55, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 56, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "這是行毀滅的臨到巴比倫。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 56, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫的勇士被捉住，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 56, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的弓折斷了；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 56, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為耶和華是施行報應的神，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 56, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必定施行報應。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 56, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 57, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "君王－名為萬軍之耶和華的說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 57, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我必使巴比倫的首領、"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 57, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "智慧人、省長、副省長，和勇士都沉醉，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 57, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "使他們睡了長覺，永不醒起。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 57, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 58, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "萬軍之耶和華如此說："}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 58, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 巴比倫寬闊的城牆必全然傾倒；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 58, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "她高大的城門必被火焚燒。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 58, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "眾民所勞碌的必致虛空；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 58, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "列國所勞碌的被火焚燒，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 58, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們都必困乏。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "耶利米的信息傳到巴比倫"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 58, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 59, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 猶大王西底家在位第四年，上巴比倫去的時候，瑪西雅的孫子、尼利亞的兒子西萊雅與王同去（西萊雅是王宮的大臣），先知耶利米有話吩咐他。 "}, {"verseNum": 60, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶利米將一切要臨到巴比倫的災禍，就是論到巴比倫的一切話，寫在書上。 "}, {"verseNum": 61, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶利米對西萊雅說：「你到了巴比倫務要念這書上的話； "}, {"verseNum": 62, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "又說：『耶和華啊，你曾論到這地方說：要剪除，甚至連人帶牲畜沒有在這裏居住的，必永遠荒涼。』 "}, {"verseNum": 63, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你念完了這書，就把一塊石頭拴在書上，扔在幼發拉底河中， "}, {"verseNum": 64, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "說：『巴比倫因耶和華所要降與她的災禍，必如此沉下去，不再興起，人民也必困乏。』」"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 64, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " 耶利米的話到此為止。"}]}]}